### Update ke config.toml

```
sed -i -e "s/^seeds *=.*/seeds = \"$SEEDS\"/; s/^persistent_peers *=.*/persistent_peers = \"$PEERS\"/" $HOME/.quicksilverd/config/config.toml
```

### Start Node

```
sudo systemctl start quicksilverd
```
